{"tid":1800152,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"用中銀嘅卡係其他銀行嘅銀通atm提款","createTime":"2019-12-27T13:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T20:10:06.000Z","uid":254330,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"775d648853f1adcd26908fa1797d7e5030b0a196","tid":1800152,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"利申一直都冇用過任何由中銀提供嘅服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一蚊都冇比佢賺過<br />\n<br />\n假設我同時有BOC同另外一間(匯豐恒生除外)銀行嘅戶口, 當係呢排好heat嘅citi啦<br />\n<br />\n咁我先將全部錢擺曬入citi, 再用BOC張卡係求其一部銀通atm拎錢, 拎幾次, 每次拎500蚊, 重複呢個動作到citi戶口冇曬錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後搵部deposit機, 存錢入去, 用手機apps transfer堆錢去citi, 再玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果人人都咁做, 會唔會蝕死中銀, 仲要不斷call車運錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好就係等緊遲到嘅仆街frd嘅時候做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 大把時間慢慢㩒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和你withdrawal<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42652a7bc0be88081ed9c26ffb2191d38b6fdebb","tid":1800152,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"775d648853f1adcd26908fa1797d7e5030b0a196","tid":1800152,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"利申一直都冇用過任何由中銀提供嘅服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一蚊都冇比佢賺過<br />\n<br />\n假設我同時有BOC同另外一間(匯豐恒生除外)銀行嘅戶口, 當係呢排好heat嘅citi啦<br />\n<br />\n咁我先將全部錢擺曬入citi, 再用BOC張卡係求其一部銀通atm拎錢, 拎幾次, 每次拎500蚊, 重複呢個動作到citi戶口冇曬錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後搵部deposit機, 存錢入去, 用手機apps transfer堆錢去citi, 再玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果人人都咁做, 會唔會蝕死中銀, 仲要不斷call車運錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好就係等緊遲到嘅仆街frd嘅時候做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 大把時間慢慢㩒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和你withdrawal<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:16:25.000Z","msg":"推唔郁都照推，順手借個位<br />\n（重要原則）想經濟攬炒，必須先紅後藍，否則只會事倍功半<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1799669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1799669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c13e55ea41c18f0782ecb776539c5916c3c58fdd","tid":1800152,"uid":4330,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"錢喺Citi點用中銀卡攞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bd848f23793dde2cec916ea15a87b783119ed9","tid":1800152,"uid":182061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:26:32.000Z","msg":"宣傳銀通畀啲藍屍，叫佢哋唔使排中銀atm，利申有個有樓親戚做咗幾十年人都唔知銀通"},{"pid":"b665ca80c762cd93665b413a040a01513e99b71f","tid":1800152,"uid":226829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:34:20.000Z","msg":"1999, <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全部錢</span>擺曬入citi&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;即係你只有citi有錢，支銀冇錢<br />\n<br />\n再用BOC張卡係求其一部銀通atm拎錢&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;咁即係你支銀戶口冇錢，咁點用BOC張卡拎錢？<br />\n<br />\n提提你：銀通網絡(基本上除匯豐恆生以外全部)係可以互相提款，如果你支銀戶口有錢，用支銀提款卡去citi櫃員機提款(或者渣打、星展、東亞、大新、永亨、富邦......都得)，咁用左citi既設施去服務非citi既支銀客，好似話citi係要向支銀畀費用既(詳情還請行內巴絲提供)，咁所以千祈唔好成日用支銀提款卡去其他銀行撳機呀！個個大量咁做，支銀好重皮架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38959c7de8bdfe698ef880aca50177e5b8c99c5","tid":1800152,"uid":5375,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"樓主應該弱智<br />\n大家唔洗理佢"},{"pid":"b00b84e92b2bf4420b8bd2ab729e95ef6a6b2021","tid":1800152,"ui